        "description": "‘E FONUAMOTU, KO ‘EKU ONGO HE TA’EMANOFO ‘A E LOTO LEULEUKEFU, HA’U KE TA Ō\nTA FOU HE PĀLAVI HINGANO FAKAVAIHOI E SĪ MELO MA’ATA TEUNGA VAHA’AKOLO KO PANGAI E KUO SŌSŌ\n‘O MANA E KAUHALALALO\n\nTANGI SI’I FĀ ‘I LO’ĀMANU\nHE ME’A MAMAHI KO E FIE ‘ALU KE U TAKAAKI HA PŌ FETAU ‘EKU KĀKANA FUOLOA ATU FU’U FILIMOTO ‘ILO ‘E HE A’U KA ME’ITE ‘A E FAKAKAUKAU HE LE’O E MANU ‘OKU VĀTAU\nHE MAKA KO FINE-TANGI-KE-TATAU\n\nMĀHINA HUHULU SI’ENE HOPO ME’A IA ‘OKU TA’EMANGALO HE TAUFETULI ‘A E HUELO\n‘O VA’INGA ‘I HE VAHA’A TONGO TAHILANU KAE NGALONGALO\n\nMĀTANGA FAKAHOLO E NOFO HA’O ‘EVA KAE MĀLŌLŌ\n‘I HE MALU ‘O PAEA-POTO\n\n‘ISA KUO TAU HOTAU HUA\nFINE VŪLANGI, HA’U KETA ‘EVA MAMATA ‘I HE NGOTO’UMU-‘A-VEKA MO E FALA-‘O-TAU-‘I-FOLAHA\n‘O HIFO KI TAHI HE TOHONANGA HAKENGA ‘O TUNUNGA MO TONGA UKU HE ‘UMEA FAINGATA’A\nKAVA EFIAFI KA TA HAKE Ā\nKE KE FOKI ‘I HE HALA TUKUTONGA LAU ‘OKU PULI KA KUO ‘ILOA\n\n(Maa’imoa ‘a Kuini Salote)"
