        "description": "TE U HIVA’AKI ‘A HOKU LOTO KE ‘ILO KOTOA ‘E HE NOFO\n‘A E FALAHOLA NA KUO HOPO ‘O MOKULU ‘I HE VAHAMAMA’O\n\nMAPA ‘O E FUNGA ‘ALAKIFONUA AFUHIA ‘E HE FISI’INAUA\nKO ‘EKU ‘OFA KO SI’O TEUNGA HA ‘AHO ‘E FAI HA TAU FONUA\n\n‘OFA ‘I HE SIU ‘A E ALAMEA PENITANI ‘O E VAKA HĒHEA ‘OKU TEKIPUNA ‘I ‘OTU ALEA MĀNOA HE FĀ-KO-FIEME’A\n\nMOTO’I SIALE ‘O FONUAMOTU TANGITANGI HE ‘API KO KOLOTOLU NGANGATU E VAI KO E FELEFONU TAUKEI ‘O LOTO KOLOFO’OU\n\nTAU\nSI’I HALA PAINI KUO LALA\n‘I HE SIUTAKA ‘A E MANU MA’A ME’APANGO KO E FELE-‘A-TOU’A ‘O TE LAKA PĒ MO TOUMOUA KUMI HOLO KUO PULI HOTO SEI ME’A NA’E FAI AI E MAHENI\nUISA KO E MONŪ TE MOU FOLAU KAU NOFO PĒ ‘O TATALI ATU\n\n(Maa’imoa ‘a Kuini Salote)"
