    {
        "title": "‘ŪPĒ ‘O ‘ULUVALU",
        "description": "MALU EFIAFI PEA TAFITONGA KA HALANI PEA HOPO E FAKAHALAFONONGA KAVEINGA ‘O E SIA-KO-KAFOA ‘OFA ATU KI LOTO NUKU’ALOFA LANGAKALI E LANGI TAU-‘A-TONGA NE MOFISI ‘I HE KAKALA ‘ILOA\n\nANGI E MATANGI HE FUNGA ‘ALAKI TOULIKI AI SI’I VAI-KO-LATAI\n\nUESIA HE FĀ PEA MAPAKI ‘O ‘ALAHA HE HALA TUPOULAHI NGA ‘A E MANUSIU ‘I PANGAI KUO TŪ’UTA ‘A E TAUTAHI\n\nFASI E PEAU HE VAHA ‘OFA HE MANATU KUO LANGA KI HE TAPA ‘A E TOFE KO LA’Ā HE KAKATO E FAKAMA’UTALA TALAPEANGALI ‘ENAU ‘EVA HE HIFONGA ‘O E FAKAMA’UNGA\n\nTAU FATULISI ‘A TOFUA TOE LAKU ‘A LOFIA HA’APAI VEU KE MANA ‘UHILA ‘E TOKI MAFOLA ATU AI E ‘IE SILIKA TAMAIKI KO HOTAU VALA FAIVA TU’U SEI ‘A VAVA’U MO HONO TAULANGA UISA HE FATAFATA MĀFANA LĒLEA MO E FĀ ‘OKU HOPO HE VAHA TUFI AI E LOTO TĀLA’A\n\n(Maa’imoa ‘a Kuini Salote) ‘UPE ‘A TU’ILOKAMANA KIA FUSIPALA\n\nTAU MATA MĀHINA FONOHAKE ‘I HE SĪ VA’INGA HE ‘ULUTOA ‘O LEA-‘A-E-TOHI ‘EVA LOTO HA’ANO MO E VAO FALAHOLA FĒFĒ SI’I MAILE HAKO ‘I HE HALATOA\n\nLAU ‘A TONGALELEKA MATALA E SIALE MO E HUNI KAUTOTO ‘O MĀHINA FEKITE KE FUNGANI AI LEVA HA FAKAMATAMOANA NGANGATU ‘OKA PO’ULI HE SISI ‘O FUSIPALA\n\nLAUMANU ‘OKU KAPA SIU ‘I MATĀHINA\n\nVĀKĒ ‘ENAU LEA ‘I HE ‘UTULA’ĀINA MAFUA ‘I HE HINGANO MATALA HE VAO HEA FAI TEUNGA MO TOLI HE FISI ‘O E TETEFA\n\n‘OFA ‘I HONAU SEI ‘OKU FAKATALUTALU TAUKEI ‘O E SEA VIEW Ē HANGAI TOKELAU MALIMALI LOTO AI PĒ TAKA HE ‘OVAVA LAHI NOFO SALUNI HE MALUMALU ‘O FULILANGI\n\n‘ISE’ISA KUO OPE HE FISI ‘O E LOSE NGA’AHOA HE TULU MAFUA ‘I OLOTELE MATALA’I HEILALA MOTO ‘O E KUKUVALU NANIVI AI MO SANI PAPAI ‘I LO’AMANU\n\nLIUAKI Ā MU’A TA’AHINE KETA ‘EVA KI HE VAO NUKONUKA ‘O E HALA TONGALEVA ‘ĀSINISINI E VAI KO TUAIKAEPAU FAKAONGOONGO AI PĒ TELEFONI HA FEKAU\n\nTAU FAKANA’A SI’I NAITE FETU’U PONGIPONGI TUITU’U HEILALA FAKAVA’E PIPI TONGI TAMAIKI PE’I TOLI TUI HONO LEIPUA KE FAKAFE’ILOAKI KI HE UAFU KO VUNA\n\n(Maa’imoa ‘a Kuini Salote)"
