    {
        "title": "‘ETE LATANOA HE HIFO MO E HAKE",
        "description": "‘ETE LATANOA HE HIFO MO E HAKE EFIAFI PEA MATALA ‘A E SIALE FĀHINA TAUKEI MATANGIMĀLIE\nKE KE TAKI ATU MU’A NA’A TE HE\nTAPA ‘A E TUPA SIO’ATA MEI HE NGŪ HOPO E LA’Ā HE ‘AHO MALŪ\nSIOFIA MĀTANGA HOLOAKI E VIŪ HE FILIMI ’ETE FAKAKAUKAU\nTAU\n‘ISE’ISA, KUO HUNI E LOLO\n‘O MAUSA HE FUNGA VEITATALO KI HE HEILALA FAKAFE’AO\nPEA KUO HOLO SI’ETE NOFO HIFOFUA KUO VEUVEU SŌ\nNAKITA FOLAU ‘A E HINGANO PE’I NOFO Ā KA MAU SOKO\nKI NUKU’ALOFA MO E FAKAUŌ\n(Maa’imoa ‘a Kuini Salote)"
