        "description": "FOTU ‘I HE LA’Ā TAPA ‘I HE LANGI MA’A\nFINE TONGA ‘OKU HAKA PEA TOLI HE KAKALA ‘O LUVA KIA VŪLANGI ‘OKA MALU EFIAFI\nAKE E MANATU AI ‘ALU KAE FOKI MAI\n\nSI’I FĀ KUO HOPO ‘O TAULUA HOKU LOTO HOTO LEI MOTELOLO LATA’ANGA ‘O E NOFO ANGI ‘A E TOKELAU PEA MOMO E PEAU\n‘O FAFANA KIA AU KAVEINGA E FOLAU\n\nFAKALAU ‘A E ATA PEA HOLO E MAMATA KI HE HUNI MO E MAPA ‘OKETI E MATALA KUO ‘EVA ‘I MOANA SI’ETE ‘OFA MAFANA HE ‘UMATA FAKALAVA ‘ASI HE TAUKAKAPA\n\nTAU\nSI’I PUA ‘ENE FISI ‘O NGAOFE HE UINI LAUKAU ‘O MAHIKI MANU-‘O-PALATAISI TU’U HIFO MU’A HE MALU ‘O E PAAME VA’INGA ‘I HE SIALE SEI ‘OHA TAKA PĒ\n\n(Maa’imoa ‘a Kuini Salote)"
