  {
    "title": "HIVA ‘O MAKAHOKOVALU",
    "description": "TOKELAU NA’E ANGI PEA HAKO ‘O FALALA HE FUNGA NIUTAO LU’IA HONO MAPO’I HINGANO NA’E MOTO ‘I ‘OUA-NA’A-NGALO\n\n‘ĀHEA MO E FĀ ‘I HE TUVA VAKAIA SI’I FETU’U KOULA\nKUO FAKAPULI ‘I HE FUTU-KO-VUNA NA’E NGANA MO E MALU’I FONUA\n\n‘E FANGA SIALE KO E TAU Ē KUO LAPA ‘A E HIKUTAMOLE ‘I HE FĀHINA E PAEPAE\nKO SI’I MAUSA ‘O E FANGATAVE\n\nHE KO LELEA TALĀ E VAI HAO’ULI AI ‘A E TOUTAI\nTE ‘OFA HE FĀFĀ-KONGA-TAHI TUKUTALA ‘OKA NUNU ‘A PANGAI\n\nTAU\nHE SIU NA KUO ‘ALAIMOANA TOUNOA SI’I LALA HEILALA ‘ALO-‘I-TALAU KO E MĀTANGA KUO FAI AI ‘APĒ HA LATA\nSEI ‘O FAFINE ‘EVA HE MAHENI HOTO PALE MOTOMOTO’I LEI\nKO E LOA NA’E TU’U HENGIHENGI KO E KAPAKAU LĒVENI\n(Maa’imoa ‘a Kuini Salote, 1948)"
  },
  {
    "title": "HIVA ‘O SIAOSI ‘ULUKIVAIOLA",
    "description": "FAKA’ISE’ISA E MATANGI TONGA LOLOMA E TOKELAU HAKONOA MAUMAU E ‘ELILI MO E LOKA\n‘I HE PULI ‘A E KAKALA ‘AONGA\n\n‘OHOVALE ‘A PALUKI PEA HANU UAFU-KO-VUNA, HĀ HA’O LAU NA’E VETE FĒFĒ FAKAMA’U\n‘O E KIE FOKOLOLO-‘O E-HA’U\n\nMALELE ‘ŌVAVA ‘O FANGASIALE MOTU E MAEA ‘A TOLUAFE\nHE SAIKOLONE NE SIAKALE VILINGIA E PAASI ‘A PAILATE\n\nFAKA’OSI FAKA’ATA E LA’AA VĀ ‘O VAVA’U PEA MO TONGA NA’E HĀ AI HONO TANGATA HAOFAKI ‘O E HIFOFUA\n\n‘OKU TALA PĒ ‘A E ‘UHINGA HE FONUALOTO KI HE VAKA TU’UTAI E FAIFATONGIA FUA TUKU’ULU HE KĀPASA\n\nTAU\n‘E ULAMOLEKA MO E TAUTAHI ‘E’AKAU’OLA, KE TALIA MAI PE KO E AVA NI ‘E PUNI ‘E HAI ‘I HE TŌ TAU ‘A E LAFITANI\nHĀ ‘A E SINO ‘O E MATEAKI NA’E TĀ TUKU PĒ HE UASI\n(Maa’imoa ‘a Kuini Salote)"
  },
  {
