    "description": "‘ATA ‘O E HAI KOULA\nNE LALANGA PEA U KAHOA\n’OU TAVANI PEA U NO’OPONA\nKA E TA KOAA KUO VETE NGOFUA\nIKU’ANGA ‘O SI’EKU TAU FĀ FELUTENI KAE NOFO PAEA\n\nKA KO’ENA ‘A E TOHI ‘O E FUAKAVA MO HOTA MAAMA KOULA SAFAILA\nTANGI E KAKALA ‘OKA EFIAFI PEA ANGIANGI IKI E MATANGI\nHANGĒ HA ‘OFA ‘OKU TULIMUI MAI\nKAE TĀ KOAA KUO SIVA ‘ETE ‘AMANAKI\nAOTEAROA KUO NGALO NGATA’A FAUNITENI KO E LO’IMATA\nMO E MATAVAI ‘O ‘ETE LOTO HOHA’A UISA Ē KUO ‘IKAI MALAVA\nPŌNGIA E LOTO NI HE MĀVAE HO’O FOLAU NE TU’UPAKEE HAKE E PEAU PEA KUO NE ‘AVE SI’OTA HUA NA’E KEI VEVELE\n‘ATU E MANATU KO HO TU’AFALA KE KUMIFONUA KI HO SINO NA\nKA KO’ENA E KAKALA KUO TAULEVA KE TOKI VETE ‘E FA’ITOKA\n\n(Maa’imoa ‘a Kuini Salote)"
